title: IPGeek
description: Quickly query geolocation, ISP, network information, and IP purity for any IP address - accurate and free
invalid_input: Invalid IP address or domain name

privacy_policy: We strictly comply with privacy protection policies (GDPR, CCPA). This service does not store any user data, does not track user behavior, and does not use cookies. All queries are processed in real-time and are immediately cleared after processing.
api_sources: This service uses data from multiple IP geolocation API providers, including: ipregistry.io, ipinfo.io, ipapi.co, ip-api.com, db-ip.com, geojs.io. The priority and availability of data sources are dynamically adjusted based on actual conditions. Map data © OpenStreetMap contributors.
